    "body": "## Purpose\nTo fix the issue on TPU introduced by https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/20775, where several new arguments in moe layer are introduced, but `forward_tpu` doesn't handle them.\n\n- fix moe layer\n- add a TPU MoE test\n\n## Test Plan\n```\npytest -s -v tests/v1/tpu/test_basic.py\n```\n\n## Test Result\nPassed\n\n## (Optional) Documentation Update\n\n<!--- pyml disable-next-line no-emphasis-as-heading -->\n",
